{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831170/extras/Gif_Wishlist_Did_You_Pick_a_Color_Yet.gif?t=1736809741\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831170/extras/ColorFear-Text_Color.png?t=1736809741\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Today on The Color Fun Coloring Show they want viewers to help them find out who is breaking into their house. Each new Intruder that breaks in has different abilities and will hunt you down! All the show wants to know is what color they show you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831170/extras/ColorFearStoryrGif.gif?t=1736809741\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831170/extras/Senr-Text_Color.png?t=1736809741\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The Night Shop:</strong>\u00a0Use the Night Shop at the end of each night to purchase upgrades or abilities to use against the color fun coloring show!\u00a0</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Upgrades that can be purchased in the Night Shop:</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A Toy Robot to help you find the location of the intruder</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A Hitman to take out your least favored of the cast members</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A Laser Cannon</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Upgrades for Flashlight and movement</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Skip a Night Card</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831170/extras/Story-Text_Color.png?t=1736809741\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Find out why</strong> Peach is making you play his twisted game each night. Delve into the mystery thriller of The Color Fun Coloring Show and why it came to be.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831170/extras/ColorFearHorrorGifs.gif?t=1736809741\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831170/extras/Horror-Text_Color.png?t=1736809741\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Designed for Fear.</strong> Intruders not only can come in at random times but can also hide and wait in the places where they know you will be going to. Each intruder has different abilities and ways they will scare you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>This is a Horror game unlike any other.</strong> Explore the deepest fears that come from The Color Fun Coloring Show.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831170/extras/Gameplay-Text_Color.png?t=1736809741\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Each night, you'll play Peaches</strong> twisted game to survive. You must follow Peaches instructions inside the house, find a specific color, and show it to Peach on the TV. But during the night. There will be intruders in the house who will hunt you down Get the color right and you'll live, Get it wrong and you're out!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Playthrough Time</strong> 72-120min</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Multiple endings</strong> depending on what you do and how you respond to your environment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Replay-ability</strong> is great with a good amount of randomization to keep every playthrough and level as fresh and scary as possible from random room spawns, intruders, buildings, tv locations and level sequences.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831170/extras/ColorFearGameplay.gif?t=1736809741\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831170/extras/Wishlist-Text_Color.png?t=1736809741\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831170/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736809741","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831170/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736809741","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831170/9ab67c5071896f90af0b49698651c7908d50e7db/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736809741","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831170/9ab67c5071896f90af0b49698651c7908d50e7db/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736809741","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3245620,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831170/extras/Gif_Wishlist_Did_You_Pick_a_Color_Yet.gif?t=1736809741\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2831170/extras/ColorFear-Text_Color.png?t=1736809741\" /></p><p class=\"bb_para